{"id":1694423,"retrievedAt":"2026-05-14T12:45:24.879Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[],"homepage":"","id":1694423,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["CL"],"original_language":"xx","original_title":"overthere: Part II","overview":"For about a dozen years, Lizama has traveled to southern Chile during the summer, mainly between the cities of Valdivia and Osorno. Years of observing birds and their collective movements, trees and their swaying, the sea and its rhythm, the rain and its whisper, the mist that turns into fog and the boats that shatter the calm. Memories and lessons embedded in cinematic time, of someone who yesterday embarked on the journey as a stranger and today does so to reach the family home. Starting from a recognizable world, we enter a more dazzling and abstract one, playing with the pixels in the frame. Recorded and (mostly) edited on a cell phone. Part II of the \"overthere\" project.","popularity":0,"poster_path":null,"production_companies":[{"id":207535,"logo_path":null,"name":"Mira Lo Que Trajo la Diligencia","origin_country":"CL"}],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"CL","name":"Chile"}],"release_date":"","revenue":0,"runtime":13,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"No Language","iso_639_1":"xx","name":"No Language"}],"status":"Released","tagline":"A FREE MOVIE","title":"overthere: Part II","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"external_ids":{"imdb_id":null,"wikidata_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"instagram_id":null,"twitter_id":null},"release_dates":{"results":[]},"credits":{"cast":[],"crew":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":4245604,"known_for_department":"Directing","name":"Gabriel Lizama (Liz Taylor)","original_name":"Gabriel Lizama","popularity":0.0071,"profile_path":"/sWJIO8h5l7jbf3CsO8gzH9lwIBJ.jpg","credit_id":"6a051ccee8baac19f5e082d6","department":"Directing","job":"Director"},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":4245